item.title: CVE-2023-41336|2023-09-11T19:21:48.938Z -- symfony -- ux-autocomplete
item.description: ux-autocomplete is a JavaScript Autocomplete functionality for Symfony. Under certain circumstances, an attacker could successfully submit an entity id for an `EntityType` that is *not* part of the valid choices. The problem has been fixed in `symfony/ux-autocomplete` version 2.11.2.
